    v1 = ((0.99 / v2) / wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.11)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.28) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.89)) * ((v2 + 0.25 * v2 + 0.86) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.57)))
    v1 = (wp.abs(v0) + tmp)
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.79 - tmp + 0.31)) / wp.exp((v2 + 0.60 - v1 + 0.40)))
